            <fr:p>We will write <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {L}{\mathopen {}\left (R\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> for the <fr:link href="jms-016M.xml" title="Formal language" addr="jms-016M" type="local">formal language</fr:link> matching or “recognised” by the regular expression <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[R]]></fr:tex>:</fr:p>
